msgstr ""

#: 20282:57
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What's going on?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:60
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Well, Mizuki-chan...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:61
msgid "Ran looked around and whispered in my ear."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:62
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What? She wants to see me?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:65
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Yeah. She's, umm... not feeling so good today.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:66
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Not feeling so good? ...Oh, that.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:67
msgid "It rang a bell right away - we'd talked about this yesterday."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:68
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Huh? Haruma-kun, do you keep track of Mizuki-chan's cycle?\""
msgstr ""

