msgid "Rin seemed surprised."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:70
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No, not the exact cycle yet. But it's a boyfriend's job to be considerate about that, right?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:71
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Wow. You've really got it together. You are a good boyfriend.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:72
msgid "Then she seemed impressed."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:73
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Well, Mizuki-chan's calling, so will you come?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:74
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Sure. I'll provide her with as much comfort as she wants.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:82
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"You're late.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:83
msgid "Mizuki greeted me in a bad mood right off the bat. I planned to comfort her, but I was a little frightened by that frown. She looked so tired as she lay in bed."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:84
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh, sorry. How are you feeling?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:87
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Do you think I'm feeling good? Ugh, uugh...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:88
msgid "She clutched her stomach and groaned."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:89
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"My stomach hurts. It feels so bad! Uugh, uugh!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:90
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Uh, umm, what should I do?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:91
msgid "I didn't have the slightest idea of what to do."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:92
msgid "In a situation like this I'm completely powerless. All I can do is watch and wait for instructions from Fujisaki-san."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:96
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Maybe you should rub her back...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:97
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Oh, okay.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:99
msgid "Just watching her pain was heartbreaking. I rushed over to sit next to her."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:100
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I hope this helps you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:101
msgid "I touched her back."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:104
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Hmm?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:105
msgid "Mizuki grunted through a sniffle. It seemed she felt a bit better from the back rub."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:109
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Simple touching can sometimes make a big difference. Maybe the human touch has some kind of magic power.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:110
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You think so?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:111
msgid "That's pretty encouraging to me. It means there should be something I can do for her."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:115
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\".........\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:116
msgid "Mizuki gave me an angry look right as I began to feel encouraged."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:117
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Do you find it more fun to talk to Rin than the bleeding, dirty me now?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:118
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"What are you talking about?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:123
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Why are you saying that?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:124
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Because...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:125
msgid "Mizuki looked upset. Even the most trivial of things seem to get on her nerves right now. I knew from my sister that sickness could make one act like that."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:126
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Jeez, you worry about such crazy things. Even if you are bleeding, you're far cuter than her!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:129
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"You see, Mizuki? Haruma-kun doesn't care about anyone but you.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:130
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Of course!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:131
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Looks like you two hit it off well.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:132
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"The hell?!\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:133
msgid "I guess nothing's going to work with her now. I'll just have to smile and nod until it passes."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:136
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Th-then I'm gonna go now. I'll leave you two alone.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:137
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Sorry.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:138
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"What are you apologizing for, Kazushi?\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:139
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yes, yes. No worries. Just close your eyes. I'm sure you'll feel a little better.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:140
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"Grr...\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:144
msgid "Fujisaki-san smiled at our exchange."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:145
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"You're so kind, Haruma-kun.\""
msgstr ""

#: 20282:146
msgid "Rin muttered it so that only I could hear. I flushed a bit."
msgstr ""

#: 20282:147
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Well, anyone can get like this when they're sick. A little selfishness every once in a while is kind of cute.\""
